# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Anki Deck Generator - API Key Configuration
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. RENAME this file from "env.template" to ".env"
# 2. Add your API keys below after the equals sign (=).
# 3. Do NOT use quotes (" or ') around your keys.
# 4. Save the file and place it in the same folder as the main application.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------


# --- REQUIRED ---
# The Gemini API is essential for all AI functions. The program will not run without it.
# Get your free Gemini API Key from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=YOUR_API_KEY_HERE


# --- OPTIONAL (for additional image sources) ---
# If you leave these blank, the corresponding image sources will be automatically disabled.

# Openverse API Key for Creative Commons images.
# Get a key by following the instructions here: https://api.openverse.engineering/v1/
OPENVERSE_API_KEY=

# Flickr API Key for Creative Commons images.
# Get a key by applying for one here: https://www.flickr.com/services/api/keys/apply/
FLICKR_API_KEY=